<ul>
<li> Jobs cannot be rescheduled if they have already been completed
<li> Jobs cannot be scheduled outside of the current month
<li> Jobs cannot be scheduled for dates in the past
<li> Some jobs may be prevented from being scheduled on certain dates
<li> Some jobs cannot be rescheduled at all once the schedule is finalized
<li>
	After the schedule is finalized, jobs can only be rescheduled within a limited window:
	<ul>
			<li> Jobs can be rescheduled up to <b>{{reschedulingWindow.past}}</b> days before their original finalization date
			<li> Jobs can be rescheduled up to <b>{{reschedulingWindow.future}}</b> days after their original finalization date
	</ul>
</li>
</ul>
